SIMPLE: needless
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Needless
<hw>Nee"dless</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Having
no need.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Weeping into the <qex>needless</qex> stream.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Not wanted; unnecessary; not requisite; <as>as,
<ex>needless</ex> labor; <ex>needless</ex> expenses.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Without sufficient cause; groundless;
causeless.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Needless</xex> jealousy.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Need"less*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Need"less*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Needlestone</ent>⟦br⟧
